                width: 200px;
                height: 100px;"> my younger and more vulnerable years my father gave me some advice that I've been turning over in my mind ever since.</div></td>
            <td class="even"></td>
            <td onreset="onReset()">
                Enter name:<input type="text" size="8">
                <input type="reset"></td>
            <td class="even"> Enter name: <input type="text" size="8" name="fname" oninvalid="onInvalid()" required><input type="submit" value="Submit"></td>
